          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "天道宗外門三千里處，上古秘境「虛空遺跡」每隔三百年開啟一次。無數修行者窮盡一生只為闖入其中，卻鮮少有人能通過第一層。這一次，秘境的開啟日期恰好和林逸的系統更新撞在了一起。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "秘境入口前，數百名修行者肅穆列隊。石壁上刻著三千年前的古文：「非有大毅力、大智慧、大機緣者，不得入內。」"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "這秘境就一個入口？排隊排到什麼時候……系統有沒有快速通道？"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "系統面板彈出一條新通知：「noclip 模式已解鎖。功能：穿牆。消耗：零。冷卻：零。」"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "穿牆？這不是經典作弊碼嗎？這遊戲居然有控制台。省得排隊了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "就在所有修行者準備正式闖關的時候，林逸面朝石壁，直接走了過去。沒有停止。沒有碰撞。他就那樣穿過了三千年無人能破的石壁，像穿過一層薄霧。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "嗯，還挺順滑的，沒有延遲。這穿牆手感不錯。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "趙小七站在秘境入口旁，手裡捧著自製的計時沙漏。自從觀察林逸以來，她養成了一個新習慣——記錄林逸做每件事的時間。沙漏上方刻著「林逸師兄行動計時器」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "師、師兄？！他、他穿過去了？！不是破壁，不是碎壁——是穿過去！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "三分鐘後，秘境深處傳來一道通知音。系統的全息公告浮現在秘境入口上方：「秘境通關。用時：三分零七秒。評價：三S。歷史最短紀錄。前三千年的最短紀錄是三年。」"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "三分鐘……三分鐘！三千年的秘境！師兄用三分鐘走完了三千年無人走通的路！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "趙小七瘋了似地翻開新筆記本，標題：《速通記錄簿：林逸師兄三分鐘破三千年秘境全紀錄》。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "虛空漫步！古籍記載，唯有超越空間法則的存在才能不破壞而穿越——師兄已經掌控了虛空法則本身！他不是在走路，他是在改寫空間！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "旁邊排隊的修行者們集體石化。有人低聲問：「那個穿牆的……是哪個宗門的？」另一人回答：「天道宗的……聽說是個外門弟子。」空氣瞬間安靜了。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene3",
    "file": "04-content3.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老作為宗門代表，原本正在秘境入口主持入場儀式。他親眼目睹了林逸穿牆的全過程。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "不……不可能……那是上古禁制石壁！連渡劫期的老夫都無法撼動分毫！他……他就走過去了？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "林逸從秘境裡走出來，手裡拿著通關獎勵——一塊系統隨機抽到的靈石碎片。"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "搞定。挺快的，就是裡面的路有點繞，幸好能穿牆，直接走直線。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "走……直線？那秘境裡有七七四十九道陣法、九九八十一道迷障！你走直線？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "linyi",
        "voice": "ryan",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "ryan",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Casual gamer tone, complains about bugs"
        },
        "text": "對啊，穿牆就沒有迷路這個問題了。反正牆擋不住我。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老！您看到了嗎！師兄的「虛空漫步」！這是空間法則的極致展現！連牆壁都不再是障礙！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老沉默了很久。他偷偷看了一眼秘境入口的石壁，又看了看自己修煉了三百年的手掌。然後，他慢慢走向石壁，伸出手，用力按了上去。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "「嗡——」石壁震動了一下，紋絲不動。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "老夫只是……檢查一下石壁的品質。例行檢查。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhaoxiaoqi",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Enthusiastic over-interpreter, warm energy"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老，您的手在抖。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoelder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "Stern elder, gradually breaking down"
        },
        "text": "那是因為……因為老夫感受到了石壁中蘊含的空間法則！對，就是這樣！老夫在感悟！"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Clear, neutral storytelling voice"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老的崩潰進度條，從百分之四十悄悄跳到了百分之四十五。三千年古壁無損，但蕭長老的尊嚴，已經開始出現裂痕。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
